  "assumptions": "<p>1. Personnel will be properly trained in HEP monitoring as well as identification of local flora.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Transects, when revisited, will be run at the same time of year and phenological stage of the indicator plants as&nbsp;the baseline transects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
